-- Holder assignment rule:
-- - User 1 and User 2 are members of the household ledger.
-- - User 3 is not a member of the household ledger.
-- - Cash accounts are shared by User 1 and User 2.
-- - Paired accounts are assigned one account to each user.
-- - Single non-cash accounts belong to User 1.
-- - JCB belongs to User 2.
